richard p mayer and james m kilts has been named president of 
kraft general foods kraft usa unit 
marsh 42 will oversee all of chicagobased whitmans 
subsidiaries including foodmaker pet inc pepsicola general 
bottlers hussmann corp and midas international 
we are all looking forward to working closely with him as we 
take the next steps in our longrange plan to increase value for 
our shareholders whitman chairman and chief executive officer 
karl bays said in a statement friday 
in 1976 marsh served as a consultant for mckinsey and co for 
five years he then served eight years with dart amp kraft in the 
united states and london 
